if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('busi_purchasedetail')
and type = 'U')
drop table busi_purchasedetail
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: busi_purchasedetail */
/*==============================================================*/
create table busi_purchasedetail (
DetailID int identity,
PurchaseID int not null,
SkuID int not null,
ProID int not null,
Link nvarchar(500) null,
SupplierID int null,
Price decimal(10,2) null,
Count int null,
Platform int null,
PackID int null,
PackgeCode nvarchar(100) null,
OutStock int null,
BadStock int null,
ErrStock int null,
DepotID int null,
IsDel int null,
constraint PK_BUSI_PURCHASEDETAIL primary key (DetailID)
)
go
